title: IPhone 7 Rumors Have Already Started
text:
Get Business & Technology Alerts 
29 Sep 2015 05:25 AM EST 
The iPhone 6S and 6S Plus launched just a few days ago â€” so of course there's already speculation about the iPhone 7. According to the Japanese Apple rumors blog Mac Otakara, several posts on China's Weibo social network suggest the next iPhone will sport a new design. The so-called iPhone 7 could be the first iPhone since the iPhone 5C to have a non-metal body and instead opt for a "frame using a new material next year." Also, the iPhone 7 could be waterproof and dustproof, but it's all just rumors for now.
